<br>
I have been collecting Brute hides and plains pebbles.  In 2 lvls I will be able to imbue them myself.<br>
<br>
Is there anyone on drinal that makes this stuff?  If so how much does it run for?  What if I provide the hides and pebbles?<br>
<br>
For those not on drinal...do any of you know the prices of this stuff? <br>
<br>
There are 4 types.. vale, imbued vale, vale reinforced, imbued vale reinforced<br>
<br>
Give wis and sta bonus' <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ulyberniabelisama.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lybernia Belisama</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.sherilyn.net/pendulum/icon.jpg BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/24/01 7:36:38 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://home.columbus.rr.com/sherilyn70/lybernia4a.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Vale Armor</span><hr size=1> I know they were asking 400p for the boots I just picked up.  Replaced my wolf fur slippers with them and made a profit. <p><img src=http://home.columbus.rr.com/sherilyn70/lybernia.GIF><BR>
